WEBVTT

00:00.357 --> 00:04.083
Here are expressions you can use for talking about thoughts and ideas.

00:06.095 --> 00:07.227
I have an idea.

00:09.105 --> 00:10.150
I've been thinking...

00:12.116 --> 00:12.951
Here's a thought.

00:14.951 --> 00:15.882
What do you think?

00:17.817 --> 00:18.797
You know what I think?

00:20.664 --> 00:22.261
I've thought about this a lot.

00:24.239 --> 00:25.811
I have no idea.

00:27.667 --> 00:28.690
I don't know.

00:30.623 --> 00:31.646
I knew it!

